text: "Strait Old Line" is a 1983 song by New Zealand art rock band Split Enz and is the leading single from their ninth studio album Conflicting Emotions. It went to number 42 in Australia and number 15 in New Zealand. ==Track listing== #"Strait Old Line" - 4:03 #"Parasite" - 3:37 ==References== Category:1983 songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Split Enz songs
